cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with shape recovery and 3D vision tasks. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is also likely as the paper addresses geometry processing and mesh super-resolution. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the paper introduces a learning-based method for shape recovery. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper uses an auto-encoder and cycle-consistent module for mapping latent vectors to eigenvalues. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is another possible category as the paper uses a neural network for shape recovery.
